## 5. Manual vs Automated Process

### Manual Process:
- Staff manually enters student data
- Sends emails individually
- Tracks seats using Excel

### Problems:
- Time-consuming
- Human errors
- Delays in communication

### Automated Process (Salesforce Flow):
- System automatically updates records
- Sends instant emails
- Real-time seat tracking

---

## 6. Reflection

### Why companies automate business processes?
Companies automate processes to save time, reduce errors, improve efficiency, and ensure consistency in operations.

Automation helps businesses scale faster and focus on important decision-making instead of repetitive tasks.

